{"tid":1596954,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"又有阿sir 擺酒，有無人去祝賀呀？","createTime":"2019-09-26T17:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T04:30:58.000Z","uid":293334,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"70ebb77b1c70d1f224db55cf141c45a5ae116e54","tid":1596954,"uid":293334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kj4Mb7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkj4Mb7a.png&h=569a349a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曹sir 9月30日係利舞台5樓星海薈擺酒喎，有無人到賀？ 阿sir 份人唔錯，你睇有人寫信嘉許。<br />\n<br />\n佢老婆就西啲，拜金女，貪小便宜，飛咗自己條仔走去溝曹sir, 因為快啲上宿舍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2zMb9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2zMb9d.jpg&h=dfc30f6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b73f8269259fd016e6912d31197a65c3cfa9037","tid":1596954,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xtttqpq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXtttqpq.jpg&h=dbc450e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd83db90b6de88ad77334be85a41162faf0aafd7","tid":1596954,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453e5bace257c18e20e092b96e2d011d576abb20","tid":1596954,"uid":177150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一對都唔會放過"},{"pid":"22e8b8db11f5b01aea851a0202f4f87cb70c5abe","tid":1596954,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:43:13.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e0ea25d6eedd7df05839fa751d2ca46394df106f","tid":1596954,"uid